Discord.js v13 was recently released and there are a few things that people may have missed out, a problem for people looking into discord.js development since most vids are from discord.js v12. So I decided to dump some stuff here!
Basically this is a summary of the most BASIC STUFF since the documentation provided is really good, this is just (re-emphasis) something for those who are new to not only discord.js, but to coding as a whole!
If you are a pretty experienced veteran, you can ignore this or you can open issues to recommend what other stuff I should add! You were probably once a noob and needed help, maybe it is your turn to help!



