Let's say you wanted to make a command that uses mentions! (Mentions are not removed or changed, but I put it here since people still ask in some forums!)

We will try to replicate the kiss command from a discord bot like owo, using discord.js (Ik many want to make currency and emote bots!)



const { Client, Intents, MessageEmbed } = require('discord.js');
const myIntents = new Intents(32767);
const client = new Client({ intents: myIntents });



